strings: <voice_0x010010B9><se_low>gone crazy: God, it's all over, I get it. I chatted with my old friends.
<voice_0x010010BA><se_low>gone crazy: The strange tree that has been seen since antiquity is called the "Tree of the Styx".
<voice_0x010010BB><se_low>gone crazy: It's easy to track and you won't notice that your registration has expired.
<voice_0x010010BC><se_low>gone crazy: But now Oldbean discovers what happened to him and goes to another world.
<voice_0x010010BD><se_low>gone crazy: Look, it's... Spitz... It's the first saber-toothed tiger to open in front of me, stubborn!
<voice_0x010010BE><se_low>gone crazy: It has made me who I am today.
<voice_0x010010BF><se_low>gone crazy: That's why I couldn't focus on leaving the office to help this old man.
<voice_0x010010C0><se_low>gone crazy: ... Good morning? Maybe me too! you do not know
<voice_0x010010C1><se_low>gone crazy: I am the director of the Big Cat Sword Foundation! Do you know why it's not helping everyone? Or at least you could!
<voice_0x010010C2><se_low>gone crazy: you know! Show that you are also part of us.
<Cap><leader> Bell is shown as a member of the Great Sword Cat Trust.
<voice_0x010010C3><se_low>gone crazy: The watch is a subscription card Clicking on the page concerned opens the adjacent subsection.
<voice_0x010010C4><se_low>gone crazy: What is the name of this fun watch? Well, actually it doesn't have a name... it's different, right?
<voice_0x010010C5><se_low>gone crazy: the cheapest! What about the song "Pumpkin Squash"? In memory of good friends and ladies!
<Cap><leader> He picked up the bell and put it in his pocket.
<voice_0x010010C6><se_low>gone crazy: Thanks a lot for your help! Don't forget the Sambreca, haha!
